Turn it into proof this week

Pick one lane (e.g., repo bug finding):
	1.	Baseline: standard prompt → measure (issues found, time)
	2.	Pantheon run: same task with skills → measure
	3.	Compare: precision, recall, time-to-fix
	4.	Publish: README + example + metrics

If it consistently beats baseline, you’ve got real compounding.

